        "title": "주다 (to request)",
        "content": [
            {
                "title": "The verb 주다 means to give, or saying please.",
                "details": "1. Appending 주다 to the end of a noun is like saying 'please give me [noun]'.<br/>2. Appending it to the end of another verb after conjugation with 아/어/여 gives it a request meaning.<br/>3. 줘 is the plain form, and 주세요 is the polite form. 드리다 is the honorific version of this verb."
            }
        ],
